When I visit /admin
I can view a list of products
And I can manage products (create, update, delete)

When I visit /admin
I can view all of the orders sorted by status (paid, canceled)
And I can update the status of any order

<h1>Admin Dashboard</h1>
<h4>{{# link-to "productNew"}}Create{{/ link-to}}, Update and Delete products</h4>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-2">
  {{# link-to "productNew" }}Create a new product{{/ link-to }}
  {{# link-to "productAll" }}View all products{{/ link-to }}
     <h4>All Products</h4>
     <ul class="list-unstyled">
      {{# each }}
      {{# if this.name }}
      <button {{ action "productDelete" this }}>Delete this product</button>
      <li> {{# link-to "productEdit" this }}
        {{ name }} ${{ format-price price }} <br>
         <img {{ bind-attr src=avatar }} class="thumbnail col-lg-12" />
         {{/ link-to }}
      <br>
      </li>
      {{/ if }}
      {{/ each }}
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-10">
   {{ outlet }}

  </div>
</div>
